location.fullValue: Savannah Plan, The Landings at Pecan Park

data.description: This 3/2/2 1532 sq ft split bedroom home in desirable Yellow Bluff Landing exudes casual elegance. The semi-open concept gives great sightlines throughout and just past the generously sized great room, the covered patio and fenced yard overlooks a peaceful pine preserve outside. Front flex room could be an office, formal dining or living area, playroom or hobby area.  The well appointed central kitchen has granite counters, an eat-in area plus breakfast bar. Owner's suite has spa-sized shower, private W/C, dual sinks and walk-in closet.  Mere minutes to Publix, River City Marketplace, Mayport Naval Station/Kings Bay, JAX Int'l Airport, the zoo, beach, cruise terminals or any of several major commuter routes. Fantastic community with wonderful amenities, too. One yr home warranty included.
